  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, I see-- because I could see for the-- to the end of the street-- I see a big truck loaded with Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, that must be it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I ran upstairs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, scram!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went everything orderly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't panic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For some reason, we never panicked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For some reason, we never panicked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we had that feeling-- if something has to happen, it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we're-- we're at ease with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we get into the closet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, [? you got ?] Germans-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Makkinje was home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when we heard her say, what is this room?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, it's for refugees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knocked on the wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they knocked on the wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And see, we're not [? found. ?] But somebody upstairs looked after us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were firm believers that somebody looked after us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they couldn't hear because it was not hollow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not hollow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, if it would have been hollow, they would have figured, well, maybe there's something inside there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would ask, well, what is in there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, that's what happened with Anne Frank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They found them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's way they got-- that's why they were arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw that movie three times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw that movie three times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "See, that was the difference in our story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no thoughts at all, no thoughts at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why I say, we were at ease with-- if something has to happen, it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were never scared, never.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It never came into our mind to be scared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As of today, I'm not scared of anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bad stomach, nervous stomach, I'm left with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But no, we were never, ever, ever scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
